## User Story
As **Diana (Dispatcher)**,
I want **depot locations visible on the map**,
So that **I can see maintenance facility distribution**.

## Acceptance Criteria

| AC | Criteria | Status |
|----|----------|--------|
| AC1 | Depot markers distinct from train markers | PASS |
| AC2 | Depot code/name shown on marker | PASS |
