## Implementation Details

### Depot Marker Design
- Square marker (vs circle for trains)
- Building icon inside
- Capacity ring around marker

### Popup Content
```
Lisboa-Entrecampos (LIS-EC)
Tracks: 8/12 (67%)
Man-hours: 450/600 (75%)
Trains: 15
```

